<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=The_Battle_of_Alexander_at_Issus&action=edit&section=11.php.html" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Notes">Notes</span></h2>
